Package: dsImaging
Type: Package
Title: DataSHIELD Clinical Imaging Platform
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("David", "Sarrat González", , "david.sarrat@isglobal.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Xavier", "Escribà-Montagut", , "xavier.escriba@isglobal.org", role = c("aut")),
      person("Juan R", "González", , "juanr.gonzalez@isglobal.org", role = c("aut")))
Description: Server-side DataSHIELD package for clinical imaging. Provides
    manifest-based dataset descriptors, storage backends, a SQLite asset
    catalog for immutable derived assets, segmentation and radiomics runners,
    model/profile registries, and DataSHIELD methods for secure imaging
    dataset management and analysis. Heavy computation is delegated to dsJobs
    as the durable HPC-capable runtime.
